headline: 3 Consumer Stocks with Warning Signs
summary: Consumer discretionary businesses are levered to the highs and lows of economic cycles. Lately, it seems like demand trends have worked in their favor as the industry has returned 31.9% over the past six months, outpacing S&P 500 by 9 percentage points.
